  <!-- EN: security door -->
  <SecurityDoor.label>安全大门</SecurityDoor.label>
  <!-- EN: Build a heavily reinforced door. It is slow to open and requires power, but is very strong. It's a good choice if you want to keep something dangerous out - or in. -->
  <SecurityDoor.description>解锁建造「安全大门」。这种经过重重加固的门开关速度较慢，且需要通电，但优点是非常坚固。若需要将危险挡在门外或锁在门内，它是个不错的选择。</SecurityDoor.description>
